Class TableSchemaPG

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mapgroup.classificator.database.dialects.TableSchema
      • com.mapgroup.classificator.database.dialects.TableSchemaPG

  •  class TableSchemaPG
extends TableSchema
    Provides utility to map PostgreSQL types to types that can be assumed by attribute.

    Every original type is mapped to string or to number.
